      "message": "This logic is partially overlapped with two other functions, readFiles and resolvePathToPaths. It\u0027s great if we can consolidate the logic.\n\nMy suggestion is to change the signature of resolvePathToPaths in the following way:\n\n // resolvePathToPaths expands a path pattern to a list of absolute paths.\n // It will resolve leading tildes and wildcards so that each resolved path can be used by os.Open.\n // If the given pattern is relative, they are considered relative to baseDir.\n func resolvePathToPaths(pattern, baseDir string) ([]string, error)\n\nThen includeFiles can be replaced with readFiles.",
